org.jhove2.core
Class I8R

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.core.I8R
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<I8R>, Reportable
@Persistent
public class I8R
extends AbstractReportable
implements Comparable<I8R>

A JHOVE2 identifier. Note that this class is named "I8R", not "IdentifierModule" to avoid confusion between "identifier" as a label and "identifier" as a process that determines a format.

Author:
mstrong, slabrams, smorrissey

                                           Class<? extends Reportable> reportableClass)
